name: oscars
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "oscars" %}
{% set version = "2.1.8" %}
{% set sha256 = "c37853089db601537c48484ee72b84ae40893daf0d4b86030e4bf080dc3965b7" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/dhidas/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 1
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"
  skip: True  # [py<36]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - matplotlib-base
    - mpi4py
    - numpy
    - scipy

test:
  imports:
    - oscars.sr
    - oscars.th
    - oscars.parametric_surfaces
    - oscars.plots_mpl
    - oscars.plots3d_mpl
    - oscars.util

about:
  home: http://oscars.bnl.gov/
  license: EPICS
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Open Source Code for Advanced Radiation Simulation
  description: The OSCARS Package.
  doc_url: https://oscars.bnl.gov/doc.php
  dev_url: https://github.com/dhidas/OSCARS

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mrakitin
    - kbeeperez
    - conda-forge/event-model
